jelio_read
_fd_ _buf_ _count_ _opt_err_

#include <jelio.h>

Unbuffered read of _count_ number of bytes from filedescripor _fd_ into the buffer _buf_.
Data read into _opt_buf_ is NOT null-terminated.
The buffer _buf_ must fit atleast _count_ number of bytes.

Returns the number of characters written into the buffer _buf_.
If an error is encountered and _opt_err_ is non-NULL *_opt_err_ is set to -1.
If no error is encountered *_opt_err_ is set to 0.

